              </div>

              <div class="flex justify-start">
                <div
                  class="p-3 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-black dark:text-white rounded-xl max-w-[70%]"
                >
                   Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit.
                  Perspiciatis culpa possimus architecto velit illum. Omnis
                  vitae cum dolore sit consectetur, expedita dicta rem porro
                  facilis nostrum maxime quidem alias impedit.
                </div>
              </div>
